{"id":275528,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/【首发】广东汕尾举行第七次数千人反贪大游行-20/","date":"2013-01-21T06:15:43Z","modified":"2013-01-21T06:15:43Z","title":"【首发】广东汕尾举行第七次数千人反贪大游行 (20图)","content":"<p><a name=\"more\"></a></p>\n<div><span>2013</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">年</span><span>1</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span><span>20</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">日，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">广东汕尾市东涌镇举行反贪污大游行，有数千人参加，大部分是妇女。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">这是从去年开始，第七次上街示威，要求政府严惩贪官，归还土地。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">上午，村民携带</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">彩色旗帜、标语、横幅，上面写着「反对贪污」、「还我土地」、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">「东涌无日月」、「团结一致」等，浩浩荡荡从东涌镇步行去汕尾市中心。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">游行队伍抵达市国土局，把许多「打倒贪官</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">还我土地」的标语牌挂在大门口的围栏上。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">中午时分队伍到达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">市政府，大批武警及防暴警察在门前广场戒备，双方保持克制，没有冲突发生。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">示威村民表示，为了给后代子孙有个交代，他们每晚都在王爷町聚集，凝聚力量，坚持到底，誓要拿回二十年来被非法倒卖的土地，及查清楚村委的糊涂帐，不达目的绝不罢休。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">东涌镇位于汕尾市城区东北部，面积</span><span>103</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">平方公里，人口</span><span>5</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">万多人。</span><span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-sgeKQWMkz-U/UPy3LlxUlyI/AAAAAAAARs8/YjX0TVFMJQ4/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-sgeKQWMkz-U/UPy3LlxUlyI/AAAAAAAARs8/YjX0TVFMJQ4/s640/1.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-iXoBtSOZbhM/UPy3NChnVuI/AAAAAAAARtE/VXF1viQfPP8/s1600/1b.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-iXoBtSOZbhM/UPy3NChnVuI/AAAAAAAARtE/VXF1viQfPP8/s640/1b.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-RP0d-Keiumg/UPy3NWM2rtI/AAAAAAAARtM/dh6rhqYT9TI/s1600/1a.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-RP0d-Keiumg/UPy3NWM2rtI/AAAAAAAARtM/dh6rhqYT9TI/s640/1a.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Ij0rr8zlqT4/UPy3O3cSIlI/AAAAAAAARtU/yDF5qiX9Oro/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Ij0rr8zlqT4/UPy3O3cSIlI/AAAAAAAARtU/yDF5qiX9Oro/s640/2.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-dtblwWhxeuA/UPy3QUsYfrI/AAAAAAAARtc/V-ic2botJqw/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-dtblwWhxeuA/UPy3QUsYfrI/AAAAAAAARtc/V-ic2botJqw/s640/3.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-4OqBCR8QT_I/UPy3QwhxzFI/AAAAAAAARtk/VA1ztD8_Jv0/s1600/5.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-4OqBCR8QT_I/UPy3QwhxzFI/AAAAAAAARtk/VA1ztD8_Jv0/s640/5.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-SiRoAxE9ZlQ/UPy3R9n3DQI/AAAAAAAARts/XZlpkOMo7a8/s1600/4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-SiRoAxE9ZlQ/UPy3R9n3DQI/AAAAAAAARts/XZlpkOMo7a8/s640/4.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-FPCLZO7xaRo/UPy3SnWFtPI/AAAAAAAARt0/ETBMbmKjsOY/s1600/6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-FPCLZO7xaRo/UPy3SnWFtPI/AAAAAAAARt0/ETBMbmKjsOY/s640/6.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-eCf2WiCtlSI/UPy3UnDagNI/AAAAAAAARt8/NbqjtoKCrpU/s1600/9.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-eCf2WiCtlSI/UPy3UnDagNI/AAAAAAAARt8/NbqjtoKCrpU/s640/9.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-CYF2ISIiUL8/UPy3Vam4CjI/AAAAAAAARuE/IcPDAsedohU/s1600/7.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogsp